reviews.review_text: Nice taste test Andrew, thanks for this and all the other fine recordings that you've made for us.  They have a depth, punch and energy you just don't get from the boards.  It's fun to also have a chance to listen from one set to another the differences with the Naks and Senns.  I love both of them, it's so hard to choose! :-)
